WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:09.400
CAPITAL

00:10.040 --> 00:11.760
Zhao Si, this is our household.

00:12.440 --> 00:14.840
I am the patriarch
and Shi Ying's elder brother.

00:15.920 --> 00:18.920
You're welcome to attend
the wedding if you want to, and if not…

00:19.000 --> 00:19.840
FIFTH MASTER, DOU SHI SHU

00:19.920 --> 00:20.840
…you're free to leave.

00:21.600 --> 00:22.560
ZHAO SI

00:22.640 --> 00:23.800
Leave?

00:27.280 --> 00:30.040
My foolish sister,
did you hear him clearly?

00:30.960 --> 00:33.600
When your husband was studying in Chanxi,

00:34.200 --> 00:37.680
he was well cared for
by your so-called best friend.

00:37.760 --> 00:39.800
And now she wants to
marry into the Dou family.

00:40.560 --> 00:42.560
And now they're having a wedding.

00:43.320 --> 00:48.280
Gu Qiu, you know how difficult it was
for me to survive alone in Chanxi,

00:48.360 --> 00:49.360
enduring all kinds of ridicule.

00:50.040 --> 00:52.520
Now that my father has been
reinstated and promoted,

00:52.600 --> 00:54.280
I could easily marry well.

00:55.160 --> 00:58.800
But I admire Shi Ying's
honesty and kindness,

00:58.880 --> 01:01.480
and I cherish the close bond we share.

01:01.560 --> 01:03.560
That's why I decided
to marry him as his concubine.

01:04.400 --> 01:07.520
It's common for officials
to have multiple wives.

01:08.800 --> 01:09.920
Better a friend

01:10.520 --> 01:13.280
than some woman you don't know,
don't you think?

01:15.520 --> 01:16.400
A friend?

01:19.680 --> 01:21.960
Is this how you repay
my trust as a friend?

01:28.560 --> 01:30.240
You knew she is my best friend,

01:32.040 --> 01:34.080
and you knew he is my husband.

01:37.600 --> 01:39.840
-How could you…
-Why couldn't they?

01:40.440 --> 01:43.040
Scholars of Shi Ying's age
already have multiple children.

01:43.760 --> 01:45.520
You've been married for nearly ten years,

01:45.600 --> 01:47.360
yet you've only given him one daughter.

01:47.440 --> 01:48.520
If he doesn't marry a concubine,

01:48.600 --> 01:52.120
are you willing to let our branch
of the family die out?

01:52.200 --> 01:54.400
Shi Shu, please stop.

01:54.480 --> 01:56.040
It's stated clearly in our law.

01:56.120 --> 01:58.080
Taking a concubine requires
the consent of the legitimate wife.

01:58.160 --> 01:59.800
My sister has every right to refuse.

01:59.880 --> 02:02.040
Young Lady Wang's father, Wang Xing Yi,

02:02.560 --> 02:05.360
is a protégé of
the Grand Secretary, Wu Yi Fen.

02:06.160 --> 02:08.120
Upon his reinstatement,
he's now a fourth-rank official.

02:08.199 --> 02:09.720
Marrying into the Wang family

02:10.639 --> 02:13.240
would be a tremendous boost
to Shi Ying's career

02:13.320 --> 02:14.160
How could she refuse?

02:14.240 --> 02:17.160
So you think my family is too
insignificant and powerless to be

02:18.280 --> 02:19.120
of any help to you now?

02:19.200 --> 02:20.400
Gu Qiu.

02:21.200 --> 02:22.440
I would never think that.

02:22.520 --> 02:25.040
The husband rules over the wife.
It's the natural order of things.

02:25.120 --> 02:27.440
Our family needs this marriage alliance.

02:28.400 --> 02:29.760
Nonsense!

02:29.840 --> 02:31.480
Over the years, how much
gold and silver has my family

02:32.080 --> 02:33.880
provided for your political connections

02:33.960 --> 02:35.720
and for Shi Ying's education?

02:35.800 --> 02:38.680
How much of it wouldn't
stand up to scrutiny?

02:39.320 --> 02:40.880
Is that your so-called natural order?

02:41.480 --> 02:43.400
If you keep pressuring my sister,

02:43.480 --> 02:47.280
I'll submit a memorial to
the court exposing everything.

02:48.200 --> 02:49.920
Zhao Si, hold your tongue!

02:50.960 --> 02:53.000
Are you really going
to ruin both our families

02:53.080 --> 02:54.720
just for your sisters?

02:54.800 --> 02:56.240
Try me.

02:57.280 --> 02:58.800
Things aren't what they used to be.

02:59.560 --> 03:00.560
If it comes to that,

03:02.000 --> 03:04.120
we'll see whose future gets cut short.

03:11.840 --> 03:13.480
I told you, didn't I?

03:13.560 --> 03:14.920
Don't worry, Shou Gu.

03:15.000 --> 03:16.280
My father will take care of it.

03:17.520 --> 03:19.400
This concerns the future
of the Dou family.

03:19.480 --> 03:21.160
Uncle Shi Shu won't give up so easily.

03:21.720 --> 03:23.400
We must resolve this quickly,

03:24.040 --> 03:26.600
or things will become much harder
once Wang Xing Yi comes.

03:28.240 --> 03:30.160
I only wanted someone to rely on.

03:30.240 --> 03:32.440
I never meant to hurt you

03:33.120 --> 03:34.280
or put Shi Ying in a difficult spot.

03:35.440 --> 03:38.080
Gu Qiu, if you really can't forgive me,

03:39.240 --> 03:40.960
grant me a white silk ribbon
so I can hang myself.

03:44.280 --> 03:46.360
Spare me the act.

03:47.240 --> 03:48.440
If you really want to die…

03:51.760 --> 03:52.960
Here.

03:53.680 --> 03:56.160
Gu Qiu, since when have you
become so cold-hearted?

04:03.480 --> 04:05.920
Ying Xue! Let go!

04:06.000 --> 04:08.160
-Ying Xue!
-Let me die!

04:08.240 --> 04:09.720
Shi Ying!

04:10.480 --> 04:12.320
Let me die!

04:14.280 --> 04:15.520
Father.

04:19.120 --> 04:19.959
Shou Gu?

04:26.560 --> 04:28.000
I missed you so much.

04:30.040 --> 04:32.240
Who is this lady on the floor?

04:32.320 --> 04:34.040
Why don't you tell Shou Gu yourself

04:35.560 --> 04:36.680
who she is?

04:38.760 --> 04:39.920
She…

04:43.320 --> 04:45.640
She's a guest here
to offer her congratulations.

04:46.640 --> 04:47.960
Shi Ying…

04:48.040 --> 04:51.800
Why are you and Mother
fighting over a guest?

04:54.560 --> 04:55.440
-We're not.
-We're not.

05:00.080 --> 05:02.200
Father, Mother.

05:04.480 --> 05:07.360
Tuo Niang, please escort this lady out.

05:08.200 --> 05:09.840
I want to talk to my parents alone.

05:10.800 --> 05:12.040
Yes, that's right.

05:12.120 --> 05:14.000
Since she's just a guest,
let's send her out first.

05:14.080 --> 05:15.880
-We will let her know our decision
-Get up.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.160
later once we've talked over it.

05:17.240 --> 05:18.600
-I'm not leaving.
-Get up.

05:18.680 --> 05:20.520
Let go of me. I'm not leaving!

05:23.680 --> 05:24.800
-She…
-Ying Xue!

05:29.280 --> 05:30.320
Ying Xue!

05:30.960 --> 05:33.640
-I can't breathe.
-It's all right. I'm right here.

05:35.160 --> 05:36.760
You're having an asthma attack.

05:38.920 --> 05:41.480
When I had a cold, Ying Xue
took care of me so closely

05:41.560 --> 05:43.880
that she ended up
developing asthma herself.

05:44.880 --> 05:45.880
Gu Qiu.

05:47.000 --> 05:48.040
I can't leave her like this.

07:20.400 --> 07:23.520
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

07:28.920 --> 07:30.360
Madam, it is the legitimate wife's duty

07:30.440 --> 07:32.040
to organize the ceremonies
for taking a concubine.

07:32.120 --> 07:33.480
Fifth Master asked me
to deliver these to you.

07:33.560 --> 07:35.680
Please make the preparations soon.

07:37.040 --> 07:38.400
Aunt hasn't even agreed to accept her!

07:38.480 --> 07:39.920
What ceremonies?

07:40.000 --> 07:41.400
Get out!

07:42.680 --> 07:45.080
Mother, as long as you don't agree,

07:45.720 --> 07:47.640
given Young Lady Wang's family background,

07:47.720 --> 07:50.160
they won't allow her to remain
an unacknowledged mistress.

07:50.760 --> 07:51.800
Even if she's fine with it,

07:51.880 --> 07:54.800
her father, Wang Xing Yi,
would never agree.

07:55.400 --> 07:56.600
If we stall long enough,

07:56.680 --> 07:58.280
the matter might quietly resolve itself.

08:01.200 --> 08:05.000
Shou Gu, how did you become so wise
at such a young age?

08:06.560 --> 08:08.600
My father says Uncle is a terrible man.

08:09.280 --> 08:11.680
It's better for you to divorce him
and avoid all this suffering.

08:14.000 --> 08:16.480
Divorce has always been seen

08:16.560 --> 08:18.440
as a trivial matter for a man,

08:19.920 --> 08:21.280
but for me and Shou Gu,

08:22.320 --> 08:24.960
it would mean being judged and
shamed for the rest of our lives.

08:26.280 --> 08:27.960
I can't ruin Shou Gu's future.

08:30.280 --> 08:32.559
Besides, after a divorce,

08:33.159 --> 08:35.240
the children always stay
with the husband's family.

08:36.159 --> 08:37.400
How could I bear to leave her?

08:38.320 --> 08:40.320
I'm not afraid of anything,

08:40.400 --> 08:41.919
except seeing you suffer.

08:42.000 --> 08:43.720
If you want to leave Father,

08:43.799 --> 08:45.080
I'll go with you.

08:45.160 --> 08:47.040
Uncle understands the law.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.240
He'll surely find a way to help.

08:48.320 --> 08:49.760
I'll go ask him.

08:50.920 --> 08:51.920
I'm coming with you.

08:54.440 --> 08:56.520
Have the kitchen prepare
tea to clear the lungs,

08:57.120 --> 08:59.200
and send someone to
dust everything in the room.

08:59.280 --> 09:01.400
-There mustn't be any trace of dust.
-Yes, Master.

09:02.040 --> 09:03.360
It's all right, Shi Ying.

09:03.960 --> 09:08.800
My sachet has ephedra to soothe my lungs.

09:08.880 --> 09:09.760
Just smelling it will help.

09:11.880 --> 09:15.600
It's just that the magnolias
in the courtyard

09:16.160 --> 09:17.680
are in full bloom.

09:19.680 --> 09:22.920
Ah, right, you can't be around pollen.

10:03.920 --> 10:06.000
Stop it! Please stop!

10:06.080 --> 10:08.120
Why are you hitting the flowers?

10:08.200 --> 10:10.920
Please just stop! Stop!

10:11.000 --> 10:13.720
-Ignore her. Don't stop.
-Stop! Stop!

10:13.800 --> 10:15.240
SERENE AND ELEGANT

10:15.320 --> 10:16.160
Seventh Madam.

10:18.320 --> 10:22.000
-Who told you to hit the flowers?
-It was me.

10:28.320 --> 10:29.360
Gu Qiu,

10:30.520 --> 10:32.160
this is just temporary measure.

10:33.640 --> 10:35.360
Is taking a concubine
a temporary measure too?

10:35.440 --> 10:36.800
Or is all this talk

10:37.680 --> 10:39.400
about heirs and your career
just an excuse?

10:41.520 --> 10:45.080
You really love her, don't you?

10:47.680 --> 10:50.240
Gu Qiu, Ying Xue has asthma.

10:50.320 --> 10:51.640
These flowers have to go.

10:54.320 --> 10:55.680
They have to go…

10:58.000 --> 10:59.160
All these years,

11:02.000 --> 11:04.960
I thought I was the only one
who could make you smile,

11:06.840 --> 11:09.440
the only one
who could weigh on your heart.

11:11.120 --> 11:12.280
I didn't realize

11:16.560 --> 11:18.120
someone else could too.

11:19.920 --> 11:21.240
I'm begging you.

11:21.320 --> 11:23.080
Please, just this once.

11:41.560 --> 11:42.560
Go ahead.

11:44.440 --> 11:45.720
Have the flowers removed.

11:48.080 --> 11:49.560
I knew you'd understand me, Gu Qiu.

11:54.440 --> 11:56.000
Thank you, Gu Qiu.

11:58.920 --> 12:00.560
Quickly! Remove the flowers!

12:00.640 --> 12:01.480
-Yes, Master!
-Get rid of them all!

12:03.720 --> 12:04.720
Remove them.

12:05.560 --> 12:06.600
Over there too.

12:08.560 --> 12:09.520
There.

12:10.680 --> 12:11.760
There, and there.

12:20.880 --> 12:23.600
The magnolia blooms without leaves

12:23.680 --> 12:25.680
When it has leaves, there are no flowers

12:25.760 --> 12:29.640
It's a symbol of purity and loyalty
Just like us.

12:30.480 --> 12:32.000
For the rest of my life

12:32.640 --> 12:34.400
I will love only you

12:37.360 --> 12:39.960
Be gentle, don't damage the branches.

12:40.560 --> 12:42.320
They'll bloom again next year.

12:44.680 --> 12:48.040
The hibiscus blooms in the morning
And falls by dusk

12:48.800 --> 12:52.200
How am I any different from the flowers?

13:05.280 --> 13:07.800
-Have some.
-I have no appetite, Zhang Ru.

13:09.680 --> 13:12.560
You must have some. Dad told me
to take good care of you.

13:22.520 --> 13:23.960
Bad man! We don't want you to push!

13:30.600 --> 13:33.440
Shou Gu, do you think
I'm a bad person too?

13:35.120 --> 13:36.440
I don't know.

13:37.040 --> 13:39.480
You made this swing for Mother.

13:39.560 --> 13:42.080
Does it belong to Young Lady Wang now?

13:44.720 --> 13:49.480
Never. This swing will always
belong to you and Gu Qiu.

13:49.560 --> 13:51.080
It won't be for anyone else.

13:51.840 --> 13:53.160
Zhang Ru and and I are small,

13:53.240 --> 13:54.600
yet even we find it crowded
sitting together.

13:54.680 --> 13:57.960
How could Mother and Young Lady Wang

13:58.040 --> 13:59.440
sit on it together and keep it steady?

14:03.000 --> 14:04.000
I know

14:04.600 --> 14:06.280
your heart has a place for Mother,

14:07.000 --> 14:09.600
but it also has a place
for Young Lady Wang.

14:09.680 --> 14:12.080
Have you ever asked yourself

14:12.160 --> 14:13.960
which weighs more?

14:17.400 --> 14:20.120
You and your mother

14:20.920 --> 14:22.320
mean more to me, of course.

14:23.560 --> 14:27.040
Then why would you rather
hurt Mother to keep her?

14:27.640 --> 14:30.720
Is… Is taking her as a concubine
really the only solution?

14:32.160 --> 14:33.440
Bad man!

14:34.640 --> 14:35.720
Shou Gu…

14:40.560 --> 14:41.600
So, you regret it now,

14:41.680 --> 14:43.520
and you want to settle this with money?

14:44.480 --> 14:46.000
If I must choose,

14:47.400 --> 14:50.640
I'd rather not hurt Gu Qiu and Shou Gu.

14:52.760 --> 14:53.760
It's too late for that.

14:54.880 --> 14:57.120
-Zou Er, tell him.
-Yes, Master.

14:57.840 --> 15:00.880
Master Shi Ying, the doctor
treating Young Lady Wang

15:01.760 --> 15:04.120
said her fainting wasn't
just due to her asthma.

15:04.200 --> 15:06.760
She's over a month pregnant.

15:13.240 --> 15:14.720
I've let Gu Qiu down.

15:15.880 --> 15:17.320
And I've let Ying Xue down too.

15:17.400 --> 15:18.520
If you don't take her in,

15:18.600 --> 15:20.760
you'll be dishonoring our father's memory.

15:21.680 --> 15:23.080
Do you remember the oath

15:23.160 --> 15:24.680
he forced us to make before he passed?

15:26.040 --> 15:27.280
To carry on the family line

15:28.720 --> 15:30.160
and restore the family's honor.

15:30.240 --> 15:31.840
At least you haven't forgotten.

15:32.560 --> 15:34.160
I've lost two wives.

15:34.960 --> 15:37.800
If I wanted to remarry,
there aren't any suitable matches left,

15:38.400 --> 15:39.880
so I've placed my hopes in you.

15:40.480 --> 15:41.760
I will treat your children

15:41.840 --> 15:44.000
like my own, and I'll personally
see to their upbringing.

15:44.600 --> 15:47.840
Shi Ying, marry her as your concubine.

15:47.920 --> 15:51.200
This will secure your career and
the continuation of our family line.

15:54.720 --> 15:55.720
Something bad has happened!

15:57.000 --> 15:58.160
Why are they shouting?

16:00.880 --> 16:03.800
Fifth Master, Seventh Master,
Seventh Madam is…

16:07.920 --> 16:09.680
PLEASANT AND CHARMING

16:16.560 --> 16:17.720
Madam…

16:18.800 --> 16:21.320
Why, Mother?

16:23.320 --> 16:24.520
Madam…

16:35.760 --> 16:37.120
Pass my order.

16:37.200 --> 16:38.400
Guard the main gate tightly.

16:38.480 --> 16:39.960
Not a word of this can get out.

16:40.040 --> 16:41.040
Yes, Master.

16:42.640 --> 16:44.120
Master.

16:50.040 --> 16:51.520
The pure magnolia blossoms

16:52.400 --> 16:54.000
remain untouched by dust or filth.

16:55.040 --> 17:00.040
Shi Ying, as flowers bloom,
they must also wither in time.

17:00.720 --> 17:02.160
Our love has run its course,

17:03.520 --> 17:04.640
and I do not blame you.

17:05.680 --> 17:08.880
But the one person I'm worried about,
the one person I feel guilty toward,

17:10.119 --> 17:11.240
is Shou Gu.

17:13.520 --> 17:15.520
I want you to protect her
for the rest of her life

17:16.480 --> 17:17.839
and never let her be wronged.

17:18.880 --> 17:20.359
You must promise me this.

17:23.160 --> 17:25.240
Mother used that to hang herself.

17:25.960 --> 17:29.080
This was the surprise
she prepared for you.

17:29.160 --> 17:30.880
It's the wine she buried
on your wedding day,

17:30.960 --> 17:33.680
praying for your success
in the imperial exams.

17:33.760 --> 17:37.880
She made your dream her own!

17:38.560 --> 17:40.640
It's my fault!

17:40.720 --> 17:42.320
I'm the one to blame!

17:42.400 --> 17:44.640
I found out that
Wang Ying Xue was pregnant,

17:44.720 --> 17:47.800
and in a moment of anger, I told Madam.

17:47.880 --> 17:49.920
-I deserve to die!
-Silence!

17:50.000 --> 17:50.960
Utter nonsense!

17:51.040 --> 17:52.440
She killed herself because
she was consumed by jealousy.

17:52.520 --> 17:54.360
It's a sin of resentment and envy.

17:54.440 --> 17:56.240
Even in death, she wants to
tarnish our family's reputation.

17:56.840 --> 17:58.040
Listen well, all of you,

17:58.120 --> 17:59.360
Zhao Gu Qiu died of illness.

18:00.120 --> 18:02.760
Anyone who dares to spread rumors
will be flogged to death!

18:03.760 --> 18:06.440
You committed adultery and
drove your legitimate wife to her death!

18:07.920 --> 18:09.960
Master Zhao, please calm down…

18:10.040 --> 18:12.320
Go ahead, celebrate your heir,
the security of your powerful ties,

18:13.080 --> 18:15.400
and marry into prestige atop her corpse!

18:17.240 --> 18:20.720
I swear I will risk my life, my honor,
and everything I have

18:20.800 --> 18:23.840
to drag you down with me!

18:25.160 --> 18:26.160
The flowers have fallen.

18:27.280 --> 18:28.280
Mother,

18:28.880 --> 18:31.960
I thought you were killed by someone.

18:32.680 --> 18:35.880
I never expected
you would end your own life

18:36.960 --> 18:38.640
because you couldn't tolerate betrayal.

18:39.640 --> 18:42.960
DOU'S RESIDENCE

18:43.040 --> 18:47.120
FUNERAL TRIBUTE

19:32.320 --> 19:33.440
My condolences.

19:33.520 --> 19:36.320
Thank you for honoring us with
your presence, Lord Li, Lord Liu.

19:37.840 --> 19:39.680
It's an unfortunate tragedy
for our family.

19:39.760 --> 19:41.960
Madam Zhao was always frail.

19:42.560 --> 19:44.280
We thought it was just a minor cold,

19:44.360 --> 19:48.080
but who could have imagined
it would take her life?

19:48.960 --> 19:53.680
Mother,
your flowers will never fall again.

20:09.560 --> 20:10.760
This place is for close family.

20:10.840 --> 20:12.560
Are you Zhao or Dou?

20:12.640 --> 20:14.000
What right do you have to be here?

20:25.480 --> 20:26.760
Shou Gu, don't cry.

20:28.800 --> 20:30.800
Your mother has passed,

20:30.880 --> 20:33.000
but I'll take her place in caring for you.

20:33.080 --> 20:35.400
I'll treat you as if you were my own.

20:40.800 --> 20:42.120
Ying Xue!

20:42.960 --> 20:43.960
Father.

20:46.160 --> 20:47.560
Now that his wife has died,

20:47.640 --> 20:49.840
Dou Shi Ying drowns himself in alcohol,

20:49.920 --> 20:51.560
wallowing in despair
and avoiding responsibility.

20:52.160 --> 20:55.080
All the criticism and blame
have fallen on you.

20:55.160 --> 20:57.840
Rather than being belittled in the future,

20:58.920 --> 21:00.600
you should come home with me.

21:01.200 --> 21:04.120
A daughter of mine would rather
remain unmarried her whole life

21:04.960 --> 21:06.120
than become a concubine.

21:06.200 --> 21:07.480
Xing Yi, you misunderstood.

21:07.560 --> 21:09.880
We've told everyone that
Madam Zhao passed away from illness.

21:10.760 --> 21:12.680
So your daughter would naturally
marry in as the legitimate wife.

21:12.760 --> 21:14.240
We'll observe all the formalities

21:14.320 --> 21:16.520
and host a grand wedding banquet
to ensure her dignity is upheld.

21:16.600 --> 21:19.680
The child she carries will be
the legitimate heir of this family,

21:19.760 --> 21:22.040
cherished and respected by all.

21:22.760 --> 21:24.560
This is our family's treasury token,

21:24.640 --> 21:26.760
which has always been held
by the household's matron.

21:26.840 --> 21:28.480
I now hand it to your daughter.

21:28.560 --> 21:30.480
She may use it as she wishes for
the dowry and wedding preparations.

21:30.560 --> 21:32.800
Madam Zhao's dowry and personal belongings

21:32.880 --> 21:34.520
will also be at her disposal.

21:34.600 --> 21:36.720
DOU'S RESIDENCE

21:38.040 --> 21:40.520
Send the inventory list to my room later.

21:40.600 --> 21:42.680
From now on, I'll review all the gifts

21:42.760 --> 21:44.720
before they're put into treasury.

21:44.800 --> 21:46.200
-Yes, Madam.
-Yes, Madam.

22:05.080 --> 22:06.040
Master Zhao,

22:06.120 --> 22:08.000
why didn't you let me
know you were coming?

22:08.680 --> 22:10.520
Perfect timing, I just made some pastries.

22:10.600 --> 22:12.520
Let Dou Zhao and Zhang Ru have some.

22:13.360 --> 22:14.880
This was part of Gu Qiu's dowry.

22:20.720 --> 22:23.160
Aunt always wore that bracelet
before she passed.

22:24.880 --> 22:26.000
Is that so?

22:30.320 --> 22:32.040
-You…
-Listen now, Zhao Si,

22:32.760 --> 22:34.080
now that Gu Qiu is gone,

22:34.160 --> 22:36.960
the bond between your family
and the Dou family is severed.

22:37.640 --> 22:40.640
I am now the rightful and legitimate wife.

22:41.560 --> 22:43.040
You may throw your weight around for now,

22:43.120 --> 22:45.520
but can you stay here forever?

22:46.320 --> 22:49.320
Aren't you worried that once you're gone,

22:49.400 --> 22:53.160
I'll take out all this anger on Dou Zhao?

22:55.720 --> 22:56.800
This is so delicious!

23:03.240 --> 23:04.880
Have some more if you like them.

23:05.800 --> 23:08.560
Just tell me what you love to eat,
and I'll make it for you.

23:08.640 --> 23:11.760
Shou Gu is still
young and naive, after all.

23:12.360 --> 23:15.440
Give her a snack,
and she forgets everything.

23:20.400 --> 23:22.880
Young Lady Wang, my stomach hurts so much!

23:24.840 --> 23:26.080
What's wrong?

23:29.960 --> 23:31.120
Shou Gu!

23:31.200 --> 23:34.520
You wicked woman,
what did you put in there? Call a doctor!

23:34.600 --> 23:36.520
Go! Go!

23:36.600 --> 23:38.120
Shou Gu, throw it up.

23:39.960 --> 23:40.960
Come on.

23:48.720 --> 23:50.000
Poor girl.

23:51.080 --> 23:52.920
You're finally awake.

23:53.600 --> 23:56.640
Shou Gu, this is Grandmother Cui.

23:56.720 --> 23:57.840
She's your grandmother.

24:00.640 --> 24:02.000
Grandmother.

24:03.560 --> 24:04.560
Give me a hand.

24:06.720 --> 24:08.400
It's no wonder Shou Gu
doesn't recognize me.

24:09.160 --> 24:12.240
I've been estranged from those
two ungrateful sons for a long time.

24:13.040 --> 24:15.960
If not for Gu Qiu writing to me
before she hanged herself,

24:16.040 --> 24:17.440
asking me to look after you,

24:17.520 --> 24:21.160
who knows how many lives they'd
destroy before they would stop?

24:22.600 --> 24:26.000
Shou Gu, what happened today?

24:26.600 --> 24:28.960
Young Lady Wang broke Mother's dowry.

24:29.960 --> 24:32.520
She said if I behaved,
I could have more pastries.

24:33.280 --> 24:36.600
The doctor said
Shou Gu was poisoned with ephedra.

24:37.320 --> 24:39.400
Ephedra is a powerful drug.

24:39.480 --> 24:41.600
For Wang Ying Xue,
who suffers from asthma,

24:41.680 --> 24:43.680
ephedra is an essential medicine.

24:43.760 --> 24:46.320
But for a child, it's a deadly poison.

24:46.840 --> 24:48.240
She's trying to wipe out all opposition

24:48.920 --> 24:50.560
and seize the family fortune.

24:50.640 --> 24:53.240
You wicked woman!
The evidence and witnesses are all here,

24:54.040 --> 24:55.120
and you still deny it?

24:55.720 --> 24:58.040
My daughter would never
stoop to such despicable acts.

24:58.720 --> 25:01.120
Let's sit down and
sort out this misunderstanding.

25:01.200 --> 25:04.240
The law clearly states

25:04.320 --> 25:06.360
that poisoning with the intent
to kill warrants execution.

25:06.440 --> 25:08.080
Even if the victim survives,

25:08.160 --> 25:10.400
the perpetrator is to receive
100 lashes and three years of labor.

25:11.000 --> 25:13.040
All three of our families are officials.

25:13.640 --> 25:15.720
If this matter reaches His Majesty's ears,

25:16.320 --> 25:18.640
could it really be dismissed
as a mere misunderstanding?

25:19.680 --> 25:20.600
I didn't poison her!

25:21.160 --> 25:23.000
I don't know how she ingested ephedra.

25:23.720 --> 25:25.840
Mother, you've lived on
the family estate for so long.

25:25.920 --> 25:28.880
How can you believe one-sided
accusations and condemn me?

25:29.480 --> 25:30.440
I refuse to accept it.

25:30.520 --> 25:33.120
Since you address Old Madam
as your mother-in-law,

25:33.200 --> 25:34.720
you shouldn't defy her authority.

25:35.400 --> 25:37.480
Old Madam is the only daughter
of the Cui family of Ji'an.

25:38.160 --> 25:39.840
Her ancestors were founding
contributors to the dynasty,

25:39.920 --> 25:41.000
honored in the imperial ancestral temple.

25:41.080 --> 25:42.800
The Cui family has been a lineage
of officials for generations.

25:42.880 --> 25:43.760
Half the court officials today

25:43.840 --> 25:46.680
were students of the Cui family academy.

25:46.760 --> 25:48.560
Considering her status and reasoning,

25:48.640 --> 25:49.480
how could you not accept her judgment?

25:50.160 --> 25:51.680
Old Madam Dou, you're actually…

25:51.760 --> 25:53.040
My surname is Cui.

25:53.120 --> 25:54.120
I do not take my husband's surname.

25:54.720 --> 25:55.600
Please sit.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.960
If this matter reaches the court,

25:58.040 --> 25:59.680
we all know how it will turn out.

25:59.760 --> 26:03.200
Lord Wang, you once risked demotion

26:03.280 --> 26:05.840
to speak out against the horse market ban,

26:05.920 --> 26:08.080
earning a reputation for integrity.

26:08.160 --> 26:10.400
But now, fresh from reinstatement,

26:10.480 --> 26:12.400
you allow your daughter
to commit such crimes.

26:12.480 --> 26:13.840
What do you think His Majesty
will make of this?

26:14.520 --> 26:15.880
Forcing a marriage,

26:15.960 --> 26:17.600
driving the legitimate wife
to hang herself,

26:17.680 --> 26:21.080
poisoning the legitimate daughter,
and seizing the family fortune,

26:21.160 --> 26:24.640
how do you propose
we settle these three charges?

26:27.960 --> 26:29.680
How do you think

26:30.680 --> 26:31.920
we should settle it, Old Madam Cui?

26:35.080 --> 26:38.440
If we and the Wang family
can settle this privately,

26:38.520 --> 26:41.600
it would provide Shou Gu
with real security.

26:41.680 --> 26:43.280
I've instructed my son

26:43.360 --> 26:44.720
to transfer all of Gu Qiu's dowry

26:44.800 --> 26:47.080
to Dou Zhao,

26:47.160 --> 26:49.080
amounting to 3,000 taels.

26:49.160 --> 26:50.960
Your family should compensate
them the same amount.

26:51.560 --> 26:52.800
That's impossible.

26:52.880 --> 26:54.680
Yours was a family of merchants.

26:55.280 --> 26:57.360
You can afford 3,000 to 5,000 taels,

26:57.440 --> 26:59.360
but my father has just been reinstated.

26:59.440 --> 27:01.520
Where could he possibly
find that kind of money?

27:01.600 --> 27:03.360
Well, he can borrow from others.

27:03.440 --> 27:05.640
Over the years, my sister
must have given you

27:05.720 --> 27:07.960
at least a hundred taels.

27:08.040 --> 27:10.800
With your father
as a fourth-ranked official,

27:10.880 --> 27:13.520
borrowing a thousand taels
shouldn't be hard.

27:13.600 --> 27:14.600
As for the rest,

27:15.520 --> 27:16.520
draft a promissory note.

27:16.600 --> 27:19.520
Whether it's five or ten years,
you will pay it off one day.

27:19.600 --> 27:21.520
But Shou Gu is so young.

27:21.600 --> 27:22.920
How can she manage all this wealth?

27:23.520 --> 27:25.880
That's not your concern, Young Lady Wang.

27:27.000 --> 27:28.960
The victim here is Shou Gu.

27:29.560 --> 27:31.200
Our opinions don't count.

27:34.280 --> 27:36.960
Go and ask her what she thinks.

27:37.720 --> 27:38.560
Yes, Old Madam.

27:46.800 --> 27:48.920
The real victim here wasn't me,

27:49.680 --> 27:50.680
it was my mother.

27:52.240 --> 27:54.200
She died with a broken heart.

27:55.840 --> 27:58.160
If Young Lady Wang marries into our family

27:58.240 --> 27:59.680
and I'm forced to call her mother,

28:01.160 --> 28:03.040
how could my own mother
ever rest in peace?

28:03.120 --> 28:05.080
Shou Gu wants Young Lady Wang

28:05.160 --> 28:09.120
to kneel in mourning for her mother
for three years and not marry into

28:09.760 --> 28:11.800
-the Dou family during that time.
-That won't do, Mother.

28:11.880 --> 28:13.080
If we don't take her in officially,

28:13.680 --> 28:15.640
how can her child
be considered legitimate?

28:15.720 --> 28:18.800
We can't allow our bloodline
to be left outside.

28:18.880 --> 28:19.960
If it's about legitimacy,

28:20.640 --> 28:22.400
a formal remarriage document will suffice.

28:22.480 --> 28:24.400
But I'm carrying your family's child.

28:25.080 --> 28:26.560
What if kneeling harms the baby?

28:26.640 --> 28:28.720
After the new wife enters the household,

28:28.800 --> 28:30.760
she will go to the Youmin Temple
for three years

28:31.760 --> 28:32.640
of reflection and repentance.

28:32.720 --> 28:35.240
Let's ensure no bad karma
falls on the child.

28:35.320 --> 28:37.000
Once the baby is born,

28:37.600 --> 28:40.880
it will be raised by a nanny
with teaching experience.

28:42.920 --> 28:45.960
Shi Ying, say something!

28:46.040 --> 28:47.680
I've wronged Gu Qiu.

28:49.040 --> 28:51.000
I'm willing to observe mourning for her

28:51.080 --> 28:52.440
and separate from my new wife.

28:53.600 --> 28:55.600
Ying Xue will go to the Youmin Temple,

28:56.320 --> 28:58.120
and I will move into Gu Qiu's room,

28:58.840 --> 29:01.480
offering incense and reciting prayers
for her day and night.

29:07.440 --> 29:08.480
I'm sorry.

29:09.080 --> 29:10.520
I've learned my lesson now.

29:11.120 --> 29:12.320
We'll pay the compensation.

29:12.920 --> 29:16.320
Please spare my child.

29:19.800 --> 29:23.000
ORCHID AND ANGELICA FOREVER FLOURISHING

29:56.400 --> 30:00.800
SERENE AND ELEGANT

30:00.880 --> 30:02.200
I'm sorry, Shou Gu.

30:03.160 --> 30:05.160
I won't be able to watch you grow up.

30:06.680 --> 30:08.960
Mother, I don't blame you.

30:14.280 --> 30:15.880
I never wanted to be your burden

30:17.240 --> 30:18.880
or watch you suffer for life.

30:20.600 --> 30:21.600
Don't worry.

30:23.240 --> 30:24.880
I'll take care of myself.

30:45.600 --> 30:46.720
The magnolias have fallen.

30:47.880 --> 30:49.120
The swing is covered in dust.

30:50.680 --> 30:52.120
This is no longer your home,

30:53.520 --> 30:54.520
nor is it mine.

30:56.760 --> 31:00.160
Mother, if your spirit lingers,

31:01.600 --> 31:03.240
may you soar beyond these high walls,

31:04.040 --> 31:05.040
past this residence,

31:06.360 --> 31:07.560
and find freedom and peace.

31:14.640 --> 31:17.920
CUI'S RESIDENCE

31:18.000 --> 31:19.320
-Madam.
-Madam.

31:19.400 --> 31:20.680
Good.

31:21.600 --> 31:23.280
ZHENDING, CUI FAMILY ESTATE

31:23.360 --> 31:24.520
It's such a beautiful estate.

31:32.640 --> 31:33.480
-Greetings, Old Madam.
-Greetings, Old Madam.

31:33.560 --> 31:35.640
-An Su, greet Old Madam.
-Greetings, Madam.

31:36.840 --> 31:38.800
This is Madam Miao and Mister Miao,

31:39.320 --> 31:40.280
neighbors from the estate.

31:43.320 --> 31:45.720
Entering a new home,
we must first dust ourselves off.

31:46.840 --> 31:48.400
Sweeping away the past

31:48.480 --> 31:50.080
brings in blessings and fortune.

31:50.680 --> 31:51.560
This is yours.

31:52.520 --> 31:53.720
And this is yours.

31:54.440 --> 31:56.400
And one for you.

31:58.120 --> 32:00.160
Grandmother, what flower is this?

32:00.800 --> 32:01.800
Nine-Layered Purple,

32:02.600 --> 32:04.440
a humble wildflower.

32:05.040 --> 32:06.920
Peonies and orchids
are delicate and beautiful,

32:07.000 --> 32:08.760
but they compete for nutrients,

32:09.360 --> 32:11.960
can't survive heavy rain and drought,

32:12.880 --> 32:14.440
and constantly need human care.

32:15.040 --> 32:16.720
Wildflowers are different.

32:16.800 --> 32:18.720
They thrive without perfect conditions.

32:18.800 --> 32:22.160
Scatter their seeds, and they'll
cover the mountains in blooms.

32:27.760 --> 32:30.880
That day, you took
the poison yourself, didn't you?

32:32.120 --> 32:33.680
Ephedra is bitter.

32:33.760 --> 32:35.040
At a toxic dose,

32:35.800 --> 32:37.920
it's so bitter that it's nearly
impossible to swallow.

32:40.400 --> 32:41.640
That child is so precocious.

32:42.680 --> 32:43.920
She must hate me to the core.

32:44.840 --> 32:46.320
She will always disobey me in the future.

32:47.200 --> 32:48.520
I must get rid of her.

32:48.600 --> 32:50.480
Young Lady, don't you have ephedra on you?

32:51.160 --> 32:53.080
That substance is harmless for adults,

32:53.160 --> 32:54.800
but children mustn't touch it.

32:54.880 --> 32:56.800
Even in tiny doses,

32:56.880 --> 32:58.200
long-term use

32:58.280 --> 33:01.480
will lead to depleted vitality
and weakened lungs.

33:02.560 --> 33:07.120
And I'll appear to be caring for her
with utmost devotion.

33:07.880 --> 33:11.400
People will see me as a virtuous wife.

33:19.720 --> 33:21.920
Wang Ying Xue was trying
to back me into a corner.

33:22.000 --> 33:23.840
Rather than waiting for her
to make her move,

33:24.720 --> 33:26.520
I chose to take the poison first

33:27.040 --> 33:28.280
to protect myself.

33:31.400 --> 33:32.320
Grandmother,

33:32.400 --> 33:34.120
I am not an evil person.

33:35.000 --> 33:36.480
To those who are kind to me,

33:36.560 --> 33:37.960
I would risk my life to repay them.

33:38.680 --> 33:39.880
But for grievances and wrongs,

33:39.960 --> 33:41.880
even if it costs me dearly,

33:41.960 --> 33:43.200
I will ensure they're repaid in full.

33:48.320 --> 33:52.240
Shou Gu, remember this,

33:54.120 --> 33:57.160
I forbid you to do such things again.

33:57.760 --> 33:59.080
I brought you out of the residence

33:59.160 --> 34:02.280
because I value
your maturity and intelligence.

34:02.360 --> 34:03.920
If you limit yourself
to petty family rivalries,

34:04.000 --> 34:06.120
you'll grow twisted and narrow-minded,

34:06.200 --> 34:08.639
confined to scheming over
a mere patch of land.

34:08.719 --> 34:11.000
You will lose sight
of the vastness of the world.

34:11.880 --> 34:15.239
I want your brilliance
to reach beyond the household,

34:15.800 --> 34:17.239
to the mountains, rivers, and lakes,

34:17.840 --> 34:19.280
and even to the country and its people.

34:19.360 --> 34:22.360
That is where you will truly shine.

34:26.480 --> 34:28.280
This is my mother's bracelet.

34:28.360 --> 34:32.320
Even something broken can shine again.

34:32.920 --> 34:37.199
Grandmother, I understand.
Coming to this estate,

34:37.280 --> 34:39.360
I've realized I don't want to
be a delicate, sheltered flower,

34:40.480 --> 34:44.040
but to become as resilient
as the Nine-Layered Purple,

34:44.120 --> 34:45.840
able to withstand wind and rain.

34:46.880 --> 34:48.040
From now on,

34:48.560 --> 34:51.080
I will live well for myself.

34:56.760 --> 34:58.520
I studied under learned masters

34:58.600 --> 34:59.800
to gain knowledge of the world.

34:59.880 --> 35:00.720
CHEN QU SHUI

35:05.320 --> 35:06.200
Will you pay or not?

35:06.840 --> 35:07.840
Do you hear me?

35:09.400 --> 35:10.400
They deserve it!

35:10.480 --> 35:12.920
Yeah!

35:13.000 --> 35:15.000
They deserve it!

35:15.080 --> 35:17.040
-They deserve it!
-Yeah!

35:24.000 --> 35:26.920
I recruited skilled maidservants
for protection.

35:32.960 --> 35:36.280
Finally, I established myself
in the world of commerce,

35:36.360 --> 35:38.000
achieving success in every venture.

35:38.080 --> 35:39.480
Hurry up.

35:56.880 --> 35:58.360
STRONG FOUNDATIONS ENSURE
NATIONAL STABILITY

36:03.600 --> 36:06.880
FUTING, DUKE OF DING'S ARMY CAMP

36:12.360 --> 36:13.360
Run!

36:14.960 --> 36:15.960
Next!

36:17.680 --> 36:21.480
DING

36:28.480 --> 36:29.520
Grand General,

36:29.600 --> 36:31.760
-a child has come to enlist.
-Faster!

36:31.840 --> 36:33.000
We guard the border

36:33.080 --> 36:35.440
so that children can stay safe at home,

36:35.520 --> 36:36.720
far from disaster.

36:36.800 --> 36:38.680
I never take in children here.
Send him away.

36:38.760 --> 36:39.680
YAN CHAO QING

36:39.760 --> 36:41.520
Grand General, please turn around
and take a look first.

36:44.000 --> 36:45.800
DUKE OF DING, JIANG MEI SUN

36:45.880 --> 36:46.720
Catch up!

36:47.440 --> 36:48.240
Grand General!

36:48.320 --> 36:49.120
YOUNG SONG MO

36:58.440 --> 36:59.440
You've come to enlist, huh?

37:00.680 --> 37:02.120
Have you lost your mind, brat?

37:02.760 --> 37:04.400
Running away from home
to join the army, huh?

37:04.480 --> 37:06.360
-Stop right there!
-Calm down now, Uncle.

37:06.440 --> 37:07.720
I didn't run away from home.

37:07.800 --> 37:08.640
I'm here to enlist for real.

37:08.720 --> 37:10.680
You think enlisting is some kind of game?

37:10.760 --> 37:12.600
Stop right there, do you hear me?

37:12.680 --> 37:15.640
Kid, if your father finds out,
he'll ground you for a year,

37:15.720 --> 37:17.000
and I won't speak up for you.

37:17.080 --> 37:18.360
You've got two choices now.

37:18.440 --> 37:20.960
Either leave on your own, or I'll
have you escorted back. Your choice.

37:21.040 --> 37:22.680
You'll have to catch me first.

37:22.760 --> 37:24.400
You're messing with me, aren't you?

37:24.480 --> 37:26.680
-Somebody, tie him up!
-Yes, sir!

37:37.400 --> 37:40.040
Grand General, we might
need more men to tie him down.

37:41.200 --> 37:43.360
I didn't think the brat
could run this fast.

37:44.960 --> 37:47.040
What are you standing here for?
Go help them!

37:47.120 --> 37:48.120
Yes, sir!

37:53.440 --> 37:54.320
Young Master.

37:56.000 --> 37:59.000
You're not even
as tall as a pirate's blade,

37:59.080 --> 38:00.880
and you're already
thinking about killing pirates?

38:02.800 --> 38:03.680
Isn't that a little…

38:05.000 --> 38:06.480
Now, am I good enough to kill them?

38:07.680 --> 38:09.720
Extraordinary! Truly extraordinary!

38:09.800 --> 38:10.880
Outrageous!

38:12.880 --> 38:13.720
Get down!

38:16.360 --> 38:17.400
Hand me the blade.

38:21.400 --> 38:23.040
Think you're so capable, do you?

38:23.640 --> 38:25.600
-Take him back home.
-Uncle!

38:26.200 --> 38:27.840
If you turn me away too,

38:28.600 --> 38:30.320
I'll truly have nowhere to go.

38:38.520 --> 38:39.880
Got kicked out by your father again?

38:42.840 --> 38:44.240
Unbelievable.

38:45.280 --> 38:47.040
What kind of father is Song Yi Chun?

38:48.040 --> 38:51.560
Uncle… No, Grand General,
please take me in.

38:52.560 --> 38:55.680
I'm ready to go through fire
and water without hesitation!

38:57.440 --> 38:58.760
Go through fire and water?

38:59.360 --> 39:00.720
Do you even know how to
start a fire and cook?

39:00.800 --> 39:01.840
A cook?

39:01.920 --> 39:03.680
-I want another role.
-If you don't want it, go now.

39:03.760 --> 39:04.800
I'll do it! I'll do it!

39:04.880 --> 39:06.080
Get to work then.

39:06.960 --> 39:09.000
Jiang Mei Sun! Just you wait!

39:09.080 --> 39:11.760
One day, I'll rise from a cook

39:11.840 --> 39:13.960
to a Grand General
who protects the nation!

39:49.480 --> 39:50.520
Give it to me!

39:55.560 --> 39:56.560
Come!

39:58.440 --> 39:59.440
Come on.

40:02.320 --> 40:03.320
Look!

40:18.240 --> 40:20.480
Zhao, you've sold off more than
half of your cloth shops

40:20.560 --> 40:22.920
and rouge stores in Guandong,

40:23.000 --> 40:25.000
only to buy dozens of silk factories
and tea estates in Futing.

40:25.680 --> 40:27.120
Although the prices were low,

40:27.200 --> 40:29.040
these are tough businesses
with thin margins.

40:29.800 --> 40:32.440
On top of that, Futing has been
plagued by pirates for years.

40:32.960 --> 40:35.080
Nine out of ten trade ships are looted.

40:35.160 --> 40:36.560
Isn't this too risky?

40:39.400 --> 40:41.560
We've reclaimed
all the islands along the coast.

40:42.560 --> 40:43.800
Cherish this,

40:43.880 --> 40:45.040
there aren't many battles left to fight.

40:53.440 --> 40:55.400
RECORD OF TRUTHS

40:58.480 --> 41:00.680
The court assigned
the Duke of Ding, Jiang Mei Sun,

41:00.760 --> 41:02.120
to pacify the seas years ago.

41:02.200 --> 41:04.560
The pirate chaos will soon be quelled,
and maritime trade will flourish.

41:05.240 --> 41:08.000
These seemingly
insignificant silks and teas

41:08.080 --> 41:09.520
will one day be worth more than gold.

41:10.200 --> 41:12.440
That's why we must secure
these businesses now.

41:12.520 --> 41:13.960
They'll bring exponential returns later.

41:14.040 --> 41:17.120
CONTRACT

41:20.800 --> 41:22.240
RECORD OF TRUTHS

41:23.920 --> 41:25.160
CLOUD-CLIMBING TRAVELER

41:25.240 --> 41:26.800
MELANCHOLY GENTLEMAN

41:28.880 --> 41:30.560
Is everything that happened in my dream

41:31.120 --> 41:32.560
destined to come true?

41:37.080 --> 41:39.880
Little one, why are you so upset?

41:40.520 --> 41:43.160
Someone actually believed
a story I made up.

41:44.640 --> 41:46.800
So, how do you like my tale?

41:47.920 --> 41:48.920
You wrote it?

41:50.680 --> 41:52.320
I've tried my best,

41:52.400 --> 41:53.880
yet why couldn't I change the outcome?

41:54.480 --> 41:56.960
Throw a stone into the river.

41:58.800 --> 42:00.240
Throw a big one,

42:00.880 --> 42:02.360
so big you can't even lift it.

42:07.160 --> 42:09.920
See, no matter how big the stone,

42:10.000 --> 42:12.120
it only creates ripples for a moment.

42:12.800 --> 42:15.600
You can't change the river's course.

42:15.680 --> 42:19.960
Then how can I change the river's course?

42:20.040 --> 42:21.320
If one day,

42:21.400 --> 42:23.640
you possess the strength

42:23.720 --> 42:26.120
to collapse the towering mountains

42:26.200 --> 42:27.560
before you,

42:28.640 --> 42:32.440
then the river's course will change.

42:46.680 --> 42:49.280
Fate is not unchangeable,

42:50.080 --> 42:51.400
nor is it insurmountable.

42:52.280 --> 42:53.320
This time,

42:53.840 --> 42:56.320
I will gain the strength
to topple mountains.

42:59.280 --> 43:00.400
I will take control

43:01.000 --> 43:02.120
of my destiny.

43:07.920 --> 43:09.320
DOU SHI SHU

43:09.400 --> 43:10.400
WANG YING XUE

43:10.480 --> 43:11.760
DOU SHI YING, UPRIGHT AS AN OFFICIAL,
COMPASSIONATE AS A FATHER

43:11.840 --> 43:13.280
JIANG MEI SUN

43:13.360 --> 43:15.240
CROWN PRINCE, PRINCE QING

43:15.320 --> 43:16.400
HIS MAJESTY

43:16.480 --> 43:18.280
DOU ZHAO

43:24.800 --> 43:30.920
SONG MO

43:43.000 --> 43:46.200
This family banquet is set up just to
let Grand Secretary Wu's eldest grandson

43:46.280 --> 43:47.760
meet the Dou family daughters, isn't it?

43:48.280 --> 43:50.440
Song Yi Chun delayed
critical military operations.

43:50.520 --> 43:51.920
Add 30 lashes.

43:52.000 --> 43:54.800
Grand General, please let me take
the punishment in my father's place.

43:54.880 --> 43:56.720
An outstanding son with a useless father!

43:56.800 --> 43:58.080
How foolish!

45:48.560 --> 45:50.680
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
